Class AbstractRegionMonitor<T extends RegionDecorator,E extends Packet>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.estimote.coresdk.observation.region.AbstractRegionMonitor<T,E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RegionMonitor<T,E>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BeaconRegionMonitor, MirrorRegionMonitor

    public abstract class AbstractRegionMonitor<T extends RegionDecorator,E extends Packet>
extends java.lang.Object
implements RegionMonitor<T,E>
    This class implements the common monitoring mechanism. Child classes are only responsible for concrete operations on different concrete regions/packets.
    Author:
    Pawel Dylag (pawel.dylag@estimote.com)
